      "startTime": 101.3708538022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk004.wav",
      "text": "ふぅん……貴方のチョイスにしては、味はまあまあね",
      "startTime": 102.8936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.7936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うわ、一瞬でボトルの半分まで減った",
      "startTime": 107.7936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor008.wav",
      "text": "説得のお供に買ってきたけど、終わるまでもつかしら",
      "startTime": 112.2936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.2269828159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "で、さあ。あんたがスリクスを解散したいのは",
      "startTime": 117.2269828159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor009.wav",
      "text": "うちじゃ、昔の相棒の宣伝を出来ないからってこと？",
      "startTime": 122.6269828159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.4936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk005.wav",
      "text": "だいぶ乱暴にまとめてくれたわね……でも、そうね",
      "startTime": 127.4936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "葉ちゃんを忘れてほしくないのに、スリクスにいても",
      "startTime": 133.1269828159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk006.wav",
      "text": "彼女のことは思い出してももらえない",
      "startTime": 136.8603161493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.5936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なら、私達で昔の曲をカバーとかすれば良くない？",
      "startTime": 139.5936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor010.wav",
      "text": "別に、そのくらいだったら付き合ってもいいわよ",
      "startTime": 145.4603161493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.5269828159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-kor011.wav",
      "text": "だからさ、そのー、解散ちょっと考え直して……",
      "startTime": 148.5269828159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ameapart-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "ameapart-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.1936494826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……急に一体、なんなのよ",
      "startTime": 154.1936494826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2508_01_02-mhk007.wav",
